videos.description: Duke's Trevon Duval enters hyper-speed and races down the court for a pretty layup that gives the Blue Devils a 13-12 lead.
videos.headline: Duval flashes speed on drive through Portland State defense

videos.description: Portland State's Jamie Orme blocks Javin DeLaurier in the lane and then leads the break as Deontae North finds open space and nails the three.
videos.headline: Portland State balling on both ends of the court

videos.description: Alex O'Connell gets the ball on the break and lobs it up for Marvin Bagley III who has no problem elevating and finishing the alley-oop.
videos.headline: Duke's Bagley throws down O'Connell lob

videos.description: Deontae North is playing confidently against the Blue Devils defense as he beats them back in transition and drains a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: North leading Portland State against Duke

videos.description: Alex O'Connell cuts to the basket on the give-and go and finishes a pretty 360-degree layup.
videos.headline: Duke's O'Connell flies through air for spinning layup

videos.description: Portland State's Deontae North has 20 points on 4-5 shooting from deep as the Vikings lead the Blue Devils 49-45 at halftime.
videos.headline: Seven first-half 3s give Portland State first-half lead over Duke

videos.description: Duke's Marvin Bagley III battles in the low post and gets rebound after rebound until he eventually finishes with the foul.
videos.headline: Bagley beasting on the boards

videos.description: Duke's Marvin Bagley III finds Trevon Duval who brings it back for the monster slam but can't finish at the rim.
videos.headline: Duval winds up and gets rejected by rim

videos.description: Duke's Grayson Allen gets to the paint and drops the ball off to Wendell Carter Jr. who gets the hoop and harm as Duke takes a 70-62 second-half lead.
videos.headline: Allen drives and dishes to for Carter and-1

videos.description: Portland State's Deontae North had 20 first-half points, but his night ends when he gets a technical foul waiting to check into the game.
videos.headline: North's electric night ends with whimper

videos.description: Physical play continues between the Vikings and Blue Devils as Grayson Allen is fouled going up for a dunk and then claps in celebration to receive a technical.
videos.headline: Chippy play continues as Allen receives technical
